## Happy Number

https://leetcode.com/problems/happy-number/

My Solution

```python
class Solution(object):

    def isHappy(self, n):
        
        def get_next(n):
            total_sum = 0 # 初始化一定要记得
            while n > 0:  # 限制loop的条件
                n, digit = divmod(n, 10) # n需要被一直迭代到最后=0才能出去
                total_sum += digit ** 2
            return total_sum
        
         seen = {}
         while n != 1 and n not in seen:
            seen.add(n)
            n = get_next(n)
        return n == 1
```
